drug.name: Trandolaprilat
drug.description: The active metabolite of the prodrug [Trandolapril].

classification.description: This compound belongs to the class of organic compounds known as dipeptides. These are organic compounds containing a sequence of exactly two alpha-amino acids joined by a peptide bond.
